

All configuration must come from environment variables.

Example .env:

NODE_ENV=production
PORT=3000

FARCASTER_APP_FID=685189
FARCASTER_PUBLIC_KEY=...

CHAIN_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.base.org
SIGNER_PRIVATE_KEY=...

STRAVA_CLIENT_ID=...
STRAVA_CLIENT_SECRET=...


Rules:

Never hardcode secrets

Never expose private keys to frontend

Backend is the trust boundary
